snippet.title: Tia TV: Teaching Amber Makeup (eye makeup for beginners)
snippet.description:
Hi guys! This is a video of Dani and I teaching Amber makeup. It's a little longer of a video, but I hope you guys like it! I definitely had a lot of fun filming this one. If you'd like to get notifications of when I upload a new video, please subscribe! Thanks you guys.
